{"tid":1492714,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】公開大學發聲明反對罷課　不贊成以罷課表達訴求","createTime":"2019-08-21T03:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T03:44:01.000Z","uid":103964,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b289abd0ea2e1d11c0cfaa839441deec8f994ea","tid":1492714,"uid":103964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"反修例】公開大學發聲明反對罷課　不贊成以罷課表達訴求<br />\n【反修例】公開大學發聲明反對罷課　不贊成以罷課表達訴求<br />\n 社會 13:48 2019/08/20  <br />\n熱門她她她的少女時代 消委會 田蕊妮 居屋2019 逃犯條例 開心速遞 抗癌新方向 星二代 港姐2019 兒童健康<br />\n 香港公開大學今日（20日）發表聲明，表示不贊成以罷課的方式表達訴求。（經濟日報資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n▲ 香港公開大學今日（20日）發表聲明，表示不贊成以罷課的方式表達訴求。（經濟日報資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》爭議未止，多間大專院校學生會擬發起9月罷課。香港公開大學今日（20日）發表聲明，表示不贊成以罷課的方式表達訴求。校方指，倘有罷課活動，會致力確保大學的教學及行政工作如常運作，以免學生的學習受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n公開大學表示，各院系處理老師及學生缺課均有其既定的做法，個別同學如在學習上遇到任何困難，可與學科的主任老師商討及尋求協助，校方會一直密切留意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n另外，樹仁大學副校監胡懷中昨日（20日）表明「同學罷課，我們不罷教」，學生不會因缺席課堂而受罰，老師亦將緊守崗位繼續授課，期間教授會盡量提供網上教育資源予同學，堅守樹仁育人的承諾使命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2431164/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E4%BB%A5%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2431164%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B4%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41De9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=34af91d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2431164/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%B4%8A%E6%88%90%E4%BB%A5%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2570749662b9d46c0df5092186d8be548867e3ec","tid":1492714,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"咁垃圾唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"22f9aececd9172f3121998b1634f19ab0b42a4af","tid":1492714,"uid":103964,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2570749662b9d46c0df5092186d8be548867e3ec","tid":1492714,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"咁垃圾唔係冇原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af1620f50b11b63ce7e33148eeaa0ac4d6b1289","tid":1492714,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"人地原本就pt讀<br />\n<br />\n有班on99就全日制讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97a4264ffe35f3702acb7344f856284f8942744","tid":1492714,"uid":94465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"成班支那人唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bd49751faf2b55cb529614d424ca9270372168","tid":1492714,"uid":50889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"鯨魚就算啦"},{"pid":"3996a40a601893f65f8cb0a91df2a7b6740c066c","tid":1492714,"uid":306413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08